Pixar Studios incredible string of commercial and critical powerhouses continued with Toy Story 3. "It hits every button from laughter to tears and lifts you up on waves of visual dazzlement. And you don't need to take a kid along to appreciate it.Tag it as one of the year's best," wrote Rolling Stone.Toy Story 3 is a 2010 American 3D computer-animated film. It is the third film in the Toy Story series. It was produced by Pixar Animation Studios and released by Walt Disney Pictures. It was directed by Lee Unkrich. Toy Story 3 was also the first film to be released theatrically with 7.1 surround sound.
